title: India breaks Fortress to seal the Series 2-1 | Thunder Downunder 4th Test Report Card #IndvsAus
tags: india vs australia live|australia vs india|test cricket live|india vs australia live match|ind vs aus live|live cricket match today|virat kohli|rishabh pant|rohit sharma|shubman gill|4th test india vs australia 2021|ashwin ravichandran|cheteshwar pujara|ajinkya rahane|rishabh pant batting|washington sundar|shardul thakur|mohammed siraj|ravi shastri|india winning moments|cheeky cheeka|kris srikkanth|anirudha srikkanth
description: What a victory for the Indian cricket Team. It has been 32 years since the Aussies lost at the gabba and it took a team with grit, determination and heart to break down the fortress to seal the series once again in Australian soil. The best part of this fairy tale was the fact that the team won it as a collective unit rather than individual brilliance. Rishab Pant is by far the most special talent in the side and the way he won the game for India was truly epic. His knock of unbeaten 89 was exemplary from the moment he went out to the middle.  Initially took his time to see the ball and once he was set he started to let loose against the bowlers. Cheeka has been saying that Rishab Pant is a match-winner for the last couple of seasons and he proved yet again why he is a special cricketer. When the day started India needed 320 odd runs to get and the initial wicket of Rohit Sharma dented all the hopes of a victory but then came in the young Gill who took the aussies bowling by surprise. What impressed Cheeka the most was the time that Shubman Gill has in the middle when he’s playing his strokes. His strokes were pristine and one thing we can say for sure about this youngster is that he is here to stay. More about him in the coming seasons. Cheteshwar pujara played the role of an anchor and the way he played his defense was simply outstanding. He got dealt a lot of lethal deliveries and also suffered a few blows but one thing he made sure of was to spend time in the wicket. The only drawback for Cheteshwar Pujara is the fact that he doesn’t seem to rotate the strike as often as he should but in today’s context, it worked for the team, and overall, it was a positive result. Overall a wonderful team effort from team India and moreover a brilliant series victory, a lot needs to be said so join us tonight live at 7.30 PM only on Cheeky Cheeka where Kris Srikkanth and Anirudha Srikkanth analyze the win to the smallest detail.Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/CheekyCheekaFollow me on:Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/cheekycheekaTwitter - https://twitter.com/KrisSrikkanthInstagram - https://www.instagram.com/cheekaofficial/Watch our Other IPL Preview Match Day Videos:👉 Match Day Live with Cheeka | Match 19 IPL 2020 RCB vs DC | Pre Match Post Match & Fantasy Predictions - https://youtu.be/HNJx5YxIA6s👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | IPL 2020 2nd Double Header | MI vs SRH | CSK vs KXIP | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions | Match 17-18 - https://youtu.be/6kESqtG2Hjs👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | IPL 2020 1st Double Header | RCB vs RR | KKR vs DC | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions | Match 15-16 - https://youtu.be/4DRTzhAQO-k👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | IPL 2020 Match 14 CSK vs SRH | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions - https://youtu.be/uneItEXuV5M👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | IPL 2020 Match 13 KXIP vs MI | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions - https://youtu.be/rjTa22wT0UM👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | IPL 2020 Match 12 RR vs KKR | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions - https://youtu.be/L1H_f83SY8s👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | IPL 2020 Match 11 SRH vs DC | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions - https://youtu.be/-iPVCUKagfo👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | MI vs RCB | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions | IPL 2020 Match 10 - https://youtu.be/sdZEqXACYg0👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | RR vs KXIP | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions | IPL 2020 Match 9 - https://youtu.be/8yepG0-XRiQ👉 Match Day Live With Cheeka | SRH vs KKR | Pre Match, Post Match & Fantasy Predictions | IPL 2020 Match 8 - https://youtu.be/DdR2BtOphwA

description: ముంబయిలో సముద్రపు ఒడ్డున ఉన్న మురికివాడలో ఉంటోంది మలీశా కుటుంబం. ప్రభుత్వ పాఠశాలలో ఏడో తరగతి చదువుతున్న ఈ అమ్మాయి  ఇంగ్లీష్ చక్కగా మాట్లాడగలదు. ద స్ట్రీట్ అనే హాలీవుడ్ చిత్రంలో నటించిన రాబర్ట్ హోఫ్‌మన్ భారత్‌లో పర్యటించినప్పుడు అనుకోకుండా మలీశాను కలిశారు. ‘ప్రిన్సెస్ ప్రమ్ ద స్లమ్’ అన్న బిరుదు ఆమెకు ఇచ్చి, ఆమెతో ఓ ఇన్‌స్ట్రాగ్రామ్ ఖాతా తెరిపించారు. కలలను సాకారం చేసుకోవడంలో మలీశాకు తోడ్పడేందుకు గో ఫండ్ మీ వెబ్‌సైట్ ద్వారా విరాళాల సేకరణ చేపట్టారు.#PrincessfromtheSlum #MaleeshaKharwa #Mumbai--- కరోనావైరస్‌ మన శరీరాన్ని ఎలా దెబ్బతీస్తుంది? వైరస్ సోకితే చనిపోయే ఆస్కారం ఎంత? వ్యాక్సీన్ ఎప్పుడు వస్తుంది? ఈ మహమ్మారికి అంతం ఎప్పుడు? – ఇలాంటి అనేక ప్రశ్నలకు సమాధానాల కోసం ఈ ప్లేలిస్టు https://bit.ly/3aiDb2A చూడండి. కరోనావైరస్‌ ఆంధ్రప్రదేశ్, తెలంగాణ రాష్ట్రాల్లో, భారతదేశంలో ఎలా వ్యాపిస్తోంది? అమెరికా, బ్రెజిల్, బ్రిటన్, ఇతర దేశాల్లో దీని ప్రభావం ఎంత తీవ్రంగా ఉంది? – ఇలాంటి అనేక అంశాలపై బీబీసీ తెలుగు వెబ్‌సైట్ కథనాల కోసం ఈ లింక్  https://bbc.in/34GUoSa క్లిక్ చేయండి. ఫేస్‌బుక్, ఇన్‌స్టాగ్రామ్, ట్విటర్‌లలో బీబీసీ తెలుగును ఫాలో అవ్వండి. ఫేస్‌బుక్: https://www.facebook.com/BBCnewsTelugu ఇన్‌స్టాగ్రామ్: https://www.instagram.com/bbcnewstelugu/ ట్విటర్: https://www.instagram.com/bbcnewstelugu/

So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:--------------------------------------------------------------------The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. tags: Madhurasrecipe|Marathi Recipe|Maharashtrian Recipes|Marathi Padarth|Maharashtrian Padarth|Marathi recipes|Dry sabzi masala|how to make masala in bulk|capsicum masala|gravy masala|bhajyansathi vatan|all purpose gravy masala|all purpose sukhi sabzi masala|all purpose gravy recipe|sukya bhajyansathi masala|dhobli mirchichi bhaji|watan lawun dhobli mirchi bhaji|shimla mirch masala|sabzi masala banane ka asan tarika|gravy recipe|sabzi masala|marathi recipes
description: #SabziMasala #WinterTreat #MadhurasRecipeसुक्या भाज्यांचा मसाला बनवण्यासाठी लागणारे साहित्य • १/४ कप बेसन • १/२ कप शेंगदाणे • थोडासा कढीपत्ता • १०~१२ लसूण पाकळ्या • १/४ कप सुकं किसलेलं खोबरं • १ चमचा जिरं • १/४ चमचा मेथ्या • १ चमचा काळा मसाला • १ चमचा लाल तिखट • चवीनुसार मीठ • १/२ चमचा साखर • २ चमचे तेल • बारीक चिरलेला कांदा • ४ मध्यम आकाराच्या चिरलेल्या ढोबळी मिरच्या • चवीनुसार मीठ • बारीक चिरलेली कोथिंबीरFollow MadhurasRecipe for more such yummy and delicious recipesSubscribe MadhurasRecipe Marathi - https://ggle.io/3QOxSubscribe MadhurasRecipe Hindi - https://ggle.io/3QOzSubscribe MadhurasRecipe - https://ggle.io/3QP1Like Facebook - https://fbook.cc/3FNzJoin Facebook group - https://fbook.cc/3GAoFollow Instagram - https://fbook.cc/3FO0https://twitter.com/madhurasrecipeWebsite - http://www.madhurasrecipe.comमधुराजरेसिपी चे मसाले ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी इथे क्लीक करा - Madhura's recipe Masala (Pack of 3)  - https://amzn.to/2L6y13iMadhurasrecipe Kanda Lasoon Masala - https://amzn.to/3okkjrPMadhurasrecipe Byadgi Mirchi Masala - https://amzn.to/3hKvRSUMadhurasrecipe Goda Masala - https://amzn.to/3hRjsg6Flipkart - https://bityl.co/4Ip9किंवा ९१३६८२२२२४ या नंबर वर व्हॉटसऍप मेसेज करा  मधुराज रेसिपी मसाले ऑर्डर कसे करायचे यासाठी हा विडिओ पहाhttps://youtu.be/9Db_owqWJe4We need dry or sukya bhajya for lunch box. There is no masala or vatan for such sabzis. For the sabzi to be tasty we need some masala for such sabzis. Here is recipe for sukya or dry sabzi masala. You can store it for about a month. You can use this masala for any dry sabzi. It tastes nice. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.Ingredients:• 1/4 cup Besan• 1/2 cup Peanuts• Few Curry leaves• 10~12 Garlic cloves• 1/4 cup shredded dry Coconut• 1 tsp Cumin seeds• 1/4 tsp Fenugreek seeds• 1 tsp Kala masala• 1 tsp Red chili powder• Salt to taste• 1/2 tsp Sugar• 2 tsp Oil• Finely chopped Onion• 4 medium size chopped Capsicum• Salt to taste• Finely chopped Coriander leavesMethod:• Heat up a pan on medium heat and add besan. • Dry roast besan a little until it begins to get light golden color. • You can add oil if you want. • Transfer the besan into a dish. • In the same pan add peanuts, curry leaves, garlic and roast everything well together. • You can skip curry leaves if you don’t like. • When peanuts are roasted well add dry coconut, cumin seeds and roast well until coconut   changes the color a little. • When coconut turns light golden, turn off the gas and add fenugreek seeds. • Transfer all the roasted ingredients into a blender jar and add kala masala, red chili powder,   salt, sugar and blend into a little coarse powder. • You can use garam masala, goda masala or any other masala that you use regularly in place   of kala masala. • You can use gudh in place of sugar or completely skip sugar too. • Masala is ready. • Heat up oil in a pan. • Add onion and fry until it turns light golden. • You can skip onion if you don’t like. • When onion begins to turn light golden add capsicum and mix well. • Cover and steam for about 6-7 minutes. • Mix well at the regular intervals of 2-3 minutes. • After about 6-7 minutes when capsicum is almost cooked add salt and mix well. • Add 2-3 tsp masala that we blended and mix well. • Cover and steam the sabzi on low heat for about 3-4 minutes.  • Add coriander leaves and mix well. • Dhobli mirachi sabzi is all ready.For more Such Recipesढोबळी मिरची  पीठ पेरून | Besan Shimla Mirch Recipe | Besan Ki Sukhi Sabzi | Capsicum with Gram flour - This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

title: 11 Women Travelling To Goa For Vacation Die In Horrifying Road Accident In Karnataka's Dharwad
tags: road accident|dharwad|dharwad accident|goa|women die in accident|truck tempo|collision|dharwad road accident|karnataka latest news|karnataka live news|tv9 kannada|kannada news|news|videos
description: women who were travelling to Goa on vacation and their driver were killed on Friday in a road accident in Karnataka’s Dharwad district after a minibus collided with a tipper truck along the Hubballi-Dharwad bypass near Itigatti. Among the deceased include the daughter-in-law of a former BJP MLA from Davangere’s Jagalur, Preethi Ravikumar. She is the daughter-in-law of former MLA Guru Siddanagouda. Dharwad Sub-urban Police Inspector Yaligar said that the accident took place around 8 am on Friday when the mini bus collided with the tipper truck, which was coming from the opposite direction. A group of 16 women from Davangere, who were members of the Ladies Club, were travelling to Goa for a vacation, when the incident occurred. The Dharwad Rural Police said that the women had decided to visit the residence of their friend in Dharwad for breakfast and had decided to take a detour. description: Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:--------------------------------------------------------------------The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.Cast:---------Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal GadaDisha Vakani as Daya Jethalal GadaRaj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal GadaShailesh Lodha as Taarak MehtaNeha Mehta as Anjali Taarak MehtaTanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam IyerMunmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan IyerMandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram BhideSonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram BhideNidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh SodhiJennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh SodhiKavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj HathiKush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)Shyam Pathak as Popatlal PandeySharad Sankla as AbdulAzhar Shaikh as Pinku Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi Special Thanks: Mahesh Vakil, Indu Tarak MehtaSet Design: Jayant DeshmukhOn-Air Promotion  ( SAB): SAB OAPCostume Designer: Alka MehtaCostume Stylist: Ekta BrahmbhattSound Recordist: Shakeel Mansuri Cameraman: Aamir ViraniProduction Head: Arvind MarchandeProduction Controler: Vinod ShishupalBackground Music: Sunil PatniOnline Editors: Vishal Tambe, Sandeep Singh Executive Producer: Jatin Yogesh BajajEditor: Dinesh GosaviCreative Supervision: Krunal KhakhkharOperation Head: Sohil RamaniWritten By: Raju Odedra & Rajen UpadhyayDirectors: Harshad Joshi, Malav Suresh RajdaTelevision Adaptation and Designed By: Asit Kumarr ModiMore Useful Links : * Like us on Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/tmkoc.sabtv* Follow us on Instagram : http://www.instagram.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmahnfp * Follow us on Twitter : http://www.twitter.com/tmkoc_ntf* Visit us at : http://www.tmkoc.com#tmkoc #taarakmehta #tmkocsmileofindia
